            <title>[JCR-1474] consistency check fails with derbypm if bundle size exceeds 32k</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1474</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>due to a &amp;#39;problem&amp;#39; in derby &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1486&quot; title=&quot; ERROR 40XD0 - When exracting Blob from a database&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;DERBY-1486&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; interleaved reads on a bundle that is larger than about 32k results in an error:&lt;br/&gt;
